entries.s_ccdcac3a: You're a brave soul. I suggest you take caution with you if you're seriously planning to go up there. Oh... and you didn't hear the information from me. I don't need the Emperor's goons coming after me.
entries.s_9f21b05a: An onslaught of recent activity at the Emperor's Retreat has the Rebel Alliance raising their eyebrows. Could the Empire be planning a large attack? Maybe you should check it out.
entries.s_68f3ba7b: I don't blame you. You don't see me going up there.
entries.s_183025b5: I think I'll go have a look.
